fields.name: Nike Essential Boyfriend T-Shirt
fields.description: Cop a casual vibe for chill days with this women's Essential Boyfriend T-Shirt from Nike. In an Archaeo Pink colorway, this tee is made from smooth, durable cotton fabric for next-level comfort. It features dropped shoulders and armholes for a relaxed feel and comes in a baggy, oversized fit for spacious wear. With a crew neckline and short sleeves in a classic cut, this tee is finished up with a Nike Swoosh to the chest. Machine washable | Our model is 5'9" and wears a size small.

fields.name: Nike Essential Long-Sleeve Mock Neck Top
fields.description: Lock in those laidback vibes with this women's Essential Long-Sleeve Mock Neck Top from Nike. In a smooth Black colorway, this tight-fit top is made from a stretchy cotton-poly fabric blend for ultra-comfy wear. It features a mock neck collar and long sleeves for full coverage and is signed off with a Nike Swoosh to the chest. Machine washable | Our model is 5'6" and wears a size small.

fields.name: adidas Originals 3-Stripes Joggers
fields.description: Sport a classic comfy look in these women's 3-Stripes Joggers from Adidas Originals. In a simple black colorway, these regular-fit joggers feature elasticated cuffs and a drawstring waist for custom wear. They're built from a soft cotton fleece for premium comfort and are finished with contrasting 3-Stripes to the side and a Trefoil logo. Machine washable. | Our model is 5'6" and wears a size small.

fields.name: Nike Essential Futura Joggers
fields.description: Level up ya off-duty looks with these women's Essential Futura Joggers from Nike. Landing in a Bronze Eclipse colourway, these regular-fit joggers are made with super-soft semi-brushed fleece for cosy comfy on chilled days. They feature an elasticated waistband with an adjustable drawcord for a custom feel, with side pockets to store ya gear when you head out. With elasticated ankle cuffs to elevate the fit, these joggers are signed off with the iconic Futura logo to the thigh. Machine washable. | Our model is 5'8" and wears a size small.

fields.name: Nike Sportswear Collection Essentials Women's Trousers
fields.description: The Nike Sportswear Trousers feature pintuck details and are a relaxed fit to help you breeze through the working week. An elastic waist and cuffs give them a comfortable, snug fit.

fields.name: JUICY COUTURE Crest Joggers
fields.description: Flex a laidback look with these women's Crest Joggers from Juicy Couture. Comin' in a fresh White colorway, these regular-fit joggers are cut from super-soft cotton fleece for supreme comfy on chilled days. They feature an elasticated waistband with an adjustable drawcord for a custom feel and have elastic cuffs at the ankles to optimize the fit and show off ya sneaks. With side pockets to store the essentials, these joggers are signed off with Juicy Couture branding in contrast to Black down the leg. Machine washable. | Our model is 5'8" and wears a size small

fields.name: JUICY COUTURE Diamante Velour Joggers
fields.description: Kick back in JD exclusive style with these women's Diamante Velour Joggers from Juicy Couture. In a Pink colorway, these joggers are made from light, stretchy poly-blend fabric for an ultra-comfy feel. They feature an elasticated waistband with an adjustable drawcord for a relaxed fit, while cuffed ankles bring an optimized fit that lets you flex your fave treads. With side pockets for storing your essentials, these joggers are signed off with "Juicy" to the reverse and silver Diamante detailing. Machine washable | Our model is 5'5" and wears a size small.

fields.name: Nike Plus Size Swoosh High Waist Leggings
fields.description: Step up your comfort with these women's Plus Size Swoosh High Waist Leggings from Nike. These tight-fit leggings come in a Black colorway and are built with a soft, durable poly-cotton blend with added stretch for comfort and freedom of movement. They feature a high-rise design and a stretchy waistband for a snug and comfortable feel. These leggings are signed off with the famous Swoosh to each thigh. Machine washable. | Our model is 5'9" and wears a size 1X.

fields.name: Nike Air Joggers Womens
fields.description: Add some Swoosh to ya' essential style with these women's Air Joggers from Nike. Comin' in a Black colorway, these regular-fit joggers are made with soft, lightweight fleece cotton for supreme comfort. They feature an elasticated waistband with an adjustable drawcord for a custom feel, and elastic to the cuffs to show off ya' creps. With side pockets for added storage, these joggers are finished up with Nike Air branding up the leg and a small logo at the thigh to sign off. Machine washable. | Our model is 5'8" and wears a size small.

fields.name: Nike Double Futura Joggers
fields.description: Step out in JD-exclusive style in these women's Double Futura Joggers from Nike. In a Regal Pink colorway, these regular-fit joggers are cut from super-smooth cotton-blended fabric with brushed fleece for a cozy feel. They feature an elasticated waistband with adjustable drawcords for a snug fit, and elastic cuffs at the ankles to hold the shape and show off ya' creps. With two side pockets, these joggers are signed off with a double Futura graphic printed to the leg. Machine washable. | Our model is 5'8" and wears a size small.

fields.name: Nike Tape Logo Fleece Joggers Womens
fields.description: Bag some off-duty style with these women's Tape Logo Fleece Joggers from Nike. Made with soft semi-brushed fleece cotton, these standard-fit joggers have a lightweight feel for comfortable everyday wear. In a Dark Grey heather colorway, these joggers have an elasticated waistband with an adjustable drawcord for a custom feel, with ribbed cuffs to show off the kicks and 2 side pockets. Finished up with Nike branded taping down the legs for a retro-inspired look and a signature Swoosh at the thigh. Machine washable. | Our model is 5'6" and wears a size small.

fields.name: Nike Essential Cargo Joggers
fields.description: Take your chill-day rotation up a notch with these women's Essential Cargo Joggers from Nike. In a Black colorway, these joggers are made using super-soft, semi-brushed fleece fabric for all-day comfort whenever you pull 'em on. They feature an elasticated, mid-rise waistband with adjustable drawcord for a relaxed, custom fit, with cuffed ankles so you can flex your fave treads. With side and cargo pockets for plenty of storage, these joggers are finished up with Nike branding on the leg. Machine washable | Our model wears a size small.

fields.name: The North Face Nuptse 1996 Jacket
fields.description: Level up on warmth with this women's Nuptse 1996 Jacket from The North Face. Inspired by the OG Nuptse, this boxy-fit jacket is made from durable, water-resistant nylon, with a cozy RDS goose down for premium warmth when the weather goes south. It comes in a blue colourway and features a full zip fastening, a raised collar, and a bungee cinch hem for custom wear. With adjustable Velcro cuffs and zipped side pockets, this coat is finished with iconic TNF branding to the chest and back in white. Machine washable. | Our model is 5'5" and wears a size small.

fields.name: Champion Logo Padded Jacket
fields.description: Keep out the cold in style with this women's Logo Padded Jacket from Champion. Coming in a Navy colorway, this padded jacket is built from lightweight poly fabric for durable comfort and has synthetic fill throughout to keep you feelin' toasty when the temperature dips. It has a full zip fastening for custom wear with a fixed hood for coverage from any downpours, the ribbed trims keep the heat locked in and the chills out. With two zippered pockets to the front for storage, this jacket is finished with famous Champion branding on the sleeve. Spot clean. | Our model is 5'7" and wears a size small

fields.name: Levis Logo Padded Jacket
fields.description: Step up your winter 'drobe with this women's Logo Padded Jacket from Levi's. In a Khaki colorway, this slim-fit jacket is made from durable poly fabric, with a lightweight yet insulated puffer design to keep you cozy. It features a full zip and button closure, as well as an adjustable toggle hood, elasticated trims, and side pockets. With toggles to cinch in the hem, this coat is finished with signature Levi's branding on the chest. Machine washable. | Our model is 5'7" and wears a size small.

fields.name: Nike Tape Jacket Womens
fields.description: Get cozy when there's a chill in the air with this women's Tape Jacket From Nike. In a Black colorway, this standard-fit jacket is made from lightweight recycled polyester with Nike Repel weather-resistant fabric to keep you dry and comfy at all times. It features Nike Therma-FIT tech to keep you warm, while the full-zip fastening, raised collar and hood provide protection from the elements. With side pockets for your essentials, this jacket is finished up with a Nike logo on the chest. Machine washable | Our model is 5'8" and wears a size small.

fields.name: JUICY COUTURE Velour Padded Jacket
fields.description: Set up for the new season in this women's Velour Padded Jacket from Juicy Couture. Comin' in a Black colorway, this oversized jacket is made with soft velour fabric for a classic JC look. Filled with synthetic down to lock in the heat, it features a full-length zipper and a funnel neckline, with a removable oversized hood for custom coverage. The sleeves have ribbed cuffs and there are adjustable bungee cords at the waist for the perf' fit. With snap-button pockets for secure storage, this jacket is finished up with a tonal logo patch at the sleeve. | Our model is 5'7" and wears a size small.

fields.name: Champion Panel Padded Jacket
fields.description: Don't let the cold stop you in your tracks with this women's Panel Padded Jacket from Champion. Coming in a White and Black colorway, this jacket is made from smooth poly fabric and has synthetic fill throughout to give you lightweight comfort and warmth. It features full zip fastening for custom wear and has a snap button closure to make sure no cold can creep in, the risen collar gives extra coverage and ribbed trims give you a snug, cozy fit. With two zippered pockets to the front for a warm place for your hands or to store your essentials, it's finished with Champion branding on the sleeve. Spot clean. | Our model wears a size small.

fields.name: adidas Badge of Sport Woven 1/4 Zip Jacket
fields.description: Be street-ready whatever the weather with this women's Badge of Sport Woven 1/4 Zip Jacket from Adidas. Coming in a Black colorway, this jacket is built from smooth, lightweight poly fabric that's fast-drying if you get caught in any downpours. It features a 1/4 zip fastening for custom airflow and a hood with adjustable drawcords for custom coverage. With elasticated cuffs for a snug fit that keeps in the heat, it's signed off with the famous Badge of Sport logo to the center of the chest. Spot clean. | Our model is 5'7" and wears a size small.

fields.name: The North Face Mountain Athletics Wind Jacket
fields.description: Cover up on cooler days with this women's Mountain Athletics Wind Jacket from The North Face. In a Black and White contrasting colorway for a stand-out look, this jacket is made from light, durable, wind-resistant polyester for warmth on blustery days. It features FlashDry moisture-wicking technology to keep you dry and comfy while meshing on the shoulders keeps air-flowing for breathability. With elasticated hems for an optimized fit and zippered pockets for secure storage, this jacket is signed off with the North Face 'Dome' logo to the chest and back. Our model is 5'6" and wears a size small.

fields.name: Columbia Puffect Padded Jacket
fields.description: Layer up and beat the cold in this women's Puffect Padded Jacket from Columbia. Comin' in a Grey colorway, this jacket is made with durable, water-resistant poly fabric and has a warming synthetic Thermarator insulation to lock in the heat. It features a full-length zipper and a funnel neckline to keep ya covered, and long sleeves with elasticated cuffs to hold 'em in place. With side pockets to store the essentials, this jacket is finished up with signature Columbia branding on the chest. | Our model is 5'6" and wears a size small.

fields.name: adidas Terrex Multi RAIN.RDY Primegreen Allover Print 2L Rain Jacket
fields.description: Showers. Wind. Sun. Or all of the above. When the forecast includes a little of everything, this adidas Terrex RAIN.RDY jacket has you covered. It seals out wet, stormy conditions, so you can get where you need to go while staying warm and dry. It's two-layer waterproof, breathable design lets you stay active and comfortable through cool, damp days. Pockets keep hands cozy and your everyday items secure. Get outside despite the weather. This product is made with Primegreen, a series of high-performance recycled materials.
